{"TopicId":37617,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Milan\u0026#039;s Helicopter(s) [Almost stock]","CreatedByName":"milankragujevic","CreatedById":49179,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-18T19:38:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"milankragujevic","CreatedById":49179,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-18T19:38:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ESupa Heliko 4\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://projects.milankragujevic.com/_keep/ksp/others/supa_heliko_img.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022supa_heliko_img.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is a coaxial type helicopter capable of flying up to 2 minutes and can carry the 3-man pod. It uses an innovative design for the rotor head, which uses the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/37707-Magic-Smoke-Industries-Parts-Infernal-Robotics\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDocking Washers mod\u003C/a\u003E as a bearing system. The mod is very lightweight and has only 5 parts. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe helicopter is easy to fly but unfortunately only has 2 channel control (up-down and spin). \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHow to use\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EDownload the mod and install it\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EDownload the craft aand put it in the VAB folder\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ELoad the craft\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EThrottle up, turn on SAS and press space\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EWhen the fuel goes empty press abort to decouple the rotor and activate parachutes\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDO NOT\u003C/strong\u003E try to land the helicopter, as rotors are slow to respond to speed changes and if you hit the ground they will hit each other\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://projects.milankragujevic.com/_keep/ksp/get.php?file=Supa_Heliko_4.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003EExpect an ION powered helicopter and a 1man pod helicopter, soon!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}